Code preview of the table Country_Bacen

USE DATABASECOUNTRYHL
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYS.SYSREFERENCES R JOIN SYS.SYSOBJECTS O ON (O.ID = R.CONSTID AND O.TYPE = 'F')
WHERE R.FKEYID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY_BACEN') AND O.NAME = 'FK_COUNTRY__COUNTRYBA_COUNTRY')
ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_BACEN
DROP CONSTRAINT FK_COUNTRY__COUNTRYBA_COUNTRY
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYSINDEXES
WHERE ID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY_BACEN')
AND NAME = 'COUNTRYBACEN_FK'
AND INDID > 0
AND INDID < 255)
DROP INDEX COUNTRY_BACEN.COUNTRYBACEN_FK
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_BACEN
DROP CONSTRAINT PK_COUNTRY_BACEN
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYSOBJECTS
WHERE ID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY_BACEN')
AND TYPE = 'U')
DROP TABLE COUNTRY_BACEN
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: COUNTRY_BACEN */
/*==============================================================*/
CREATE TABLE COUNTRY_BACEN (
CBA_ID INT IDENTITY,
COU_ID INT NOT NULL,
CBA_CODIGO INT NOT NULL
)
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_BACEN
ADD CONSTRAINT PK_COUNTRY_BACEN PRIMARY KEY (CBA_ID)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: COUNTRYBACEN_FK */
/*==============================================================*/




CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX COUNTRYBACEN_FK ON COUNTRY_BACEN (COU_ID ASC)
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_BACEN
ADD CONSTRAINT FK_COUNTRY__COUNTRYBA_COUNTRY FOREIGN KEY (COU_ID)
REFERENCES COUNTRY (COU_ID)
go
